nfo: [Deployment](https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html)\n","slug":"hello-world","published":1,"date":"2019-08-22T07:07:34.150Z","updated":"2019-08-22T07:07:34.150Z","comments":1,"layout":"post","photos":[],"link":"","_id":"cjzo1hahf0000z4w6oyfgrjjj","content":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a href=\"#Quick-Start\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#Create-a-new-post\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Create a new post\"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">\"My New Post\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\"><a href=\"#Run-server\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Run server\"></a>Run server</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\"><a href=\"#Generate-static-files\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Generate static files\"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\"><a href=\"#Deploy-to-remote-sites\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Deploy to remote sites\"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Deployment</a></p>\n","site":{"data":{}},"excerpt":"","more":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a href=\"#Quick-Start\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#Create-a-new-post\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Create a new post\"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">\"My New Post\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\"><a href=\"#Run-server\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Run server\"></a>Run server</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\"><a href=\"#Generate-static-files\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Generate static files\"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\"><a href=\"#Deploy-to-remote-sites\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Deploy to remote sites\"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Deployment</a></p>\n"},{"title":"Android开发 ScrollView默认位置不是最顶部解决方案","date":"2017-01-22T04:49:59.000Z","_content":"\n## 描述：\nScrollview里面嵌套了一个listview ，这是开发中最寻常的一种布局，遇到的问题是：在这个Scrollview页面默认的起始位置不是最顶部，而是listview的底部。\n\n------\n## 原因：\n1. 在Activity计算窗口的高度时，是在listview没有填充数据时候就完成的，由于ScrollView嵌套listview时没有指定高度，所以ScrollView就会按照layout中定义的默认高度计算。\n\n2. 因为listview获取了焦点。\n\n----\n## 解决：\n1. myScrollView.smoothScrollTo(0,20);\n >需在listview数据加载完成后调用\n\n2. 在代码里去掉listview的焦点\n>lv.setFocusable(false);\n\n3. Listview外套一层LinearLayout\n\n4. 跟EditText一样，在父元素的属性下面下下面这两行即可\n>android:focusableInTouchMode=\"true\"\nandroid:focusable=\"true\"\n\n5. 最开始的时候让最上面其中一个控件获得焦点，滚动条自然就到顶部去了，如下：\n>txtBaseMsg.setFocusable(true);\ntxtBaseMsg.setFocusableInTouchMode(true);\ntxtBaseMsg.requestFocus();","source":"_posts/test.md","raw":"---\ntitle: Android开发 ScrollView默认位置不是最顶部解决方案\ndate: 2017-01-22 12:49:59\ntags:\n---\n\n## 描述：\nScrollview里面嵌套了一个listview ，这是开发中最寻常的一种布局，遇到的问题是：在这个Scrollview页面默认的起始位置不是最顶部，而是listview的底部。\n\n------\n## 原因：\n1. 在Activity计算窗口的高度时，是在listview没有填充数据时候就完成的，由于ScrollView嵌套listview时没有指定高度，所以ScrollView就会按照layout中定义的默认高度计算。\n\n2. 因为listview获取了焦点。\n\n----\n## 解决：\n1. myScrollView.smoothScrollTo(0,20);\n >需在listview数据加载完成后调用\n\n2. 在代码里去掉listview的焦点\n>lv.setFocusable(false);\n\n3. Listview外套一层LinearLayout\n\n4. 跟EditText一样，在父元素的属性下面下下面这两行即可\n>android:focusableInTouchMode=\"true\"\nandroid:focusable=\"true\"\n\n5. 最开始的时候让最上面其中一个控件获得焦点，滚动条自然就到顶部去了，如下：\n>txtBaseMsg.setFocusable(true);\ntxtBaseMsg.setFocusableInTouchMode(true);\ntxtBaseMsg.requestFocus();","slug":"test","published":1,"updated":"2019-08-22T10:15:48.459Z","comments":1,"layout":"post","photos":[],"link":"","_id":"cjzo1hahj0001z4w6snvm0x7r","content":"<h2 id=\"描述：\"><a href=\"#描述：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"描述：\"></a>描述：</h2><p>Scrollview里面嵌套了一个listview ，这是开发中最寻常的一种布局，遇到的问题是：在这个Scrollview页面默认的起始位置不是最顶部，而是listview的底部。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"原因：\"><a href=\"#原因：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"原因：\"></a>原因：</h2><ol>\n<li><p>在Activity计算窗口的高度时，是在listview没有填充数据时候就完成的，由于ScrollView嵌套listview时没有指定高度，所以ScrollView就会按照layout中定义的默认高度计算。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>因为listview获取了焦点。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"解决：\"><a href=\"#解决：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解决：\"></a>解决：</h2><ol>\n<li><p>myScrollView.smoothScrollTo(0,20);</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>需在listview数据加载完成后调用</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li><p>在代码里去掉listview的焦点</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>lv.setFocusable(false);</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li><p>Listview外套一层LinearLayout</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>跟EditText一样，在父元素的属性下面下下面这两行即可</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>android:focusableInTouchMode=”true”<br>android:focusable=”true”</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li><p>最开始的时候让最上面其中一个控件获得焦点，滚动条自然就到顶部去了，如下：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>txtBaseMsg.setFocusable(true);<br>txtBaseMsg.setFocusableInTouchMode(true);<br>txtBaseMsg.requestFocus();</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ol>\n","site":{"data":{}},"excerpt":"","more":"<h2 id=\"描述：\"><a href=\"#描述：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"描述：\"></a>描述：</h2><p>Scrollview里面嵌套了一个listview ，这是开发中最寻常的一种布局，遇到的问题是：在这个Scrollview页面默认的起始位置不是最顶部，而是listview的底部。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"原因：\"><a href=\"#原因：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"原因：\"></a>原因：</h2><ol>\n<li><p>在Activity计算窗口的高度时，是在listview没有填充数据时候就完成的，由于ScrollView嵌套listview时没有指定高度，所以ScrollView就会按照layout中定义的默认高度计算。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>因为listview获取了焦点。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"解决：\"><a href=\"#解决：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解决：\"></a>解决：</h2><ol>\n<li><p>myScrollView.smoothScrollTo(0,20);</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>需在listview数据加载完成后调用</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li><p>在代码里去掉listview的焦点</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>lv.setFocusable(false);</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li><p>Listview外套一层LinearLayout</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>跟EditText一样，在父元素的属性下面下下面这两行即可</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>android:focusableInTouchMode=”true”<br>android:focusable=”true”</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li><p>最开始的时候让最上面其中一个控件获得焦点，滚动条自然就到顶部去了，如下：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>txtBaseMsg.setFocusable(true);<br>txtBaseMsg.setFocusableInTouchMode(true);<br>txtBaseMsg.requestFocus();</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ol>\n"}],"PostAsset":[],"PostCategory":[],"PostTag":[],"Tag":[]}}